@database TransferAnimClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - TransferAnim Class"


TransferAnim class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The TransferAnim class is a subclass of Area class and it is
  used to display transfer or busy animations as known from
  browsers.

  TransferAnim is a subclass of TransferAnim.mcc so you must have
  TransferAnim.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use it. TransferAnim.mcc is
  copyright of Linus McCabe.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}TABoingBall@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}TAChanges@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}TADefObjHeight@{fg text}
  N I

  @{fg shine}TADefObjWidth@{fg text}
